ActBroadcasting Act
PrecisAppointment of RITA SHELTON DEVERELL, C.M., of Coldwater, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Broadcasting Corporation, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective November 28, 2020, in the place of Robert Jeffery, whose term has expired.
